title: Trump-Kim talks 'some weeks' away - Tillerson
text:
Trump-Kim talks 'some weeks' away - Tillerson Friday, March 09, 2018 - 01:13 
U.S. Secretary of State Rex Tillerson says U.S. President Donald Trump is prepared to meet North Korean leader Kim Jong Un. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
